ont-size:36pt;padding-bottom:6pt;font-family:"Roboto";line-height:1.5;page-break-after:avoid;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:justify}.subtitle{padding-top:18pt;color:#666666;font-size:24pt;padding-bottom:4pt;font-family:"Georgia";line-height:1.5;page-break-after:avoid;font-style:italic;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:justify}li{color:#000000;font-size:10pt;font-family:"Roboto"}p{margin:0;color:#000000;font-size:10pt;font-family:"Roboto"}h1{padding-top:6pt;color:#000000;font-weight:700;font-size:10pt;padding-bottom:6pt;font-family:"Roboto";line-height:1.5;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:justify}h2{padding-top:6pt;color:#000000;font-weight:700;font-size:10pt;padding-bottom:6pt;font-family:"Roboto";line-height:1.5;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:justify}h3{padding-top:6pt;color:#000000;font-weight:700;font-size:10pt;padding-bottom:6pt;font-family:"Roboto";line-height:1.5;page-break-after:avoid;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:justify}h4{padding-top:2pt;color:#0f4761;font-size:10pt;padding-bottom:0pt;font-family:"Play";line-height:1.5;page-break-after:avoid;font-style:italic;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:justify}h5{padding-top:2pt;color:#0f4761;font-size:10pt;padding-bottom:0pt;font-family:"Play";line-height:1.5;page-break-after:avoid;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:justify}h6{padding-top:2pt;color:#0a2f40;font-size:10pt;padding-bottom:0pt;font-family:"Play";line-height:1.5;page-break-after:avoid;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:justify}</style></head><body class="c58 doc-content"><p class="c32 c27"><span class="c6 c37"></span></p><table class="c114"><tr class="c47"><td class="c60" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c32 c51"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 230.40px; height: 123.53px;"><img alt="" src="images/image3.png" style="width: 230.40px; height: 123.53px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p></td><td class="c74" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c32 c27"><span class="c59 c10 c42"></span></p><p class="c32"><span class="c10 c42 c59">&nbsp; Direcci&oacute;n Territorial de Educaci&oacute;n, Cultura y Universidades de Alicante</span></p><p class="c32"><span class="c2 c42 c67">&nbsp; Secci&oacute;n de Gesti&oacute;n de Centros-Equipo de Becas y T&iacute;tulos</span></p><p class="c32"><span class="c10 c91">&nbsp; C</span><span class="c2">/ </span><span class="c59 c10 c42">Carratal&agrave;, 47 &ndash; 03007 &ndash; ALICANTE</span></p><p class="c32"><span class="c10 c91">&nbsp; Becas.espe_ali@gva.es &nbsp;</span><span class="c10 c106"><a class="c48" href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.ceice.gva.es/&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1781200428541983&amp;usg=AOvVaw0FiHhvCtueo5-gU-keL5IA">www.ceice.gva.es</a></span><span class="c10 c91">&nbsp; </span></p></td></tr></table><p class="c63 c51 c68"><span class="c6 c102">DOCUMENTO 3: MEMORIA ECON&Oacute;MICA JUSTIFICATIVA DEL PAGO DEL SERVICIO RECIBIDO</span></p><p class="c32 c63 c116 c51 c118"><span class="c6 c78 c10">(A cumplimentar por el centro o reeducador en el que el alumnado ha recibido el servicio para el que se solicit&oacute; la ayuda.</span></p><p class="c63 c27 c51 c104"><span class="c6 c85"></span></p><p class="c63 c27 c111"><span class="c6 c78 c10"></span></p><p class="c31"><span class="c66">Resoluci&oacute;n de la secretar&iacute;a de estado de educaci&oacute;n, por la que se convocan ayudas para alumnos con necesidad espec&iacute;fica de apoyo educativo para el curso acad&eacute;mico 2025-2026, de 23 de abril de 2025 (BOE, 25 de abril de 2025). Art&iacute;culo 20 (</span><span class="c66 c92">Control sobre el cumplimiento de la finalidad de la ayuda y reintegros</span><span class="c66">), apartado 3: &ldquo;En el caso de las ayudas para reeducaci&oacute;n pedag&oacute;gica, reeducaci&oacute;n del lenguaje y/o ayudas para alumnos con altas capacidades intelectuales, estas tareas de comprobaci&oacute;n se llevar&aacute;n a cabo por los &oacute;rganos de selecci&oacute;n a que se refiere el art&iacute;culo 16 de esta Resoluci&oacute;n. A estos efectos, </span><span class="c1">se requerir&aacute; la presentaci&oacute;n por el interesado de los justificantes del pago del servicio recibido</span><span class="c6 c22">&rdquo;.</span></p><p class="c11"><span class="c6 c22"></span></p><p class="c11"><span class="c6 c22"></span></p><p class="c11"><span class="c6 c22"></span></p><p class="c31"><span class="c6 c22">1. Identificaci&oacute;n del prestador de servicios (nombre del profesional/centro, raz&oacute;n social, NIF, domicilio):</span></p><p class="c11"><span class="c6 c22"></span></p><table class="c72"><tr class="c81"><td class="c41" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c75"><span class="c6 c78 c112">Mar&iacute;a Dolores Riquelme Garc&iacute;a &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;NIF: 33479511K<br>Pedagoga / Maestra de Audici&oacute;n y Lenguaje</span></p><p class="c75"><span class="c6 c78 c112">N&ordm; Colegiada: 2443<br>Gabinete DISAHC<br>C/ Jorge Juan, 36, Entlo. Dcha.<br>03201 Elche</span></p></td></tr></table><p class="c11"><span class="c6 c22"></span></p><p class="c11"><span class="c6 c22"></span></p><p class="c11"><span class="c6 c22"></span></p><p class="c36"><span class="c6 c22">2. Alumna/alumno que ha recibido los servicios:</span></p><table class="c33"><tr class="c30"><td class="c46" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c34"><span class="c10">Nombre y Apellidos: </span><span class="c12">{{NOMBRE}}</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c30"><td class="c46" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c34"><span class="c10">DNI/NIF: </span><span class="c10 c70">&nbsp;</span><span class="c12">{{DNI}}</span></p></td></tr></table><p class="c11"><span class="c6 c22"></span></p><p class="c11"><span class="c6 c22"></span></p><p class="c11"><span class="c6 c22"></span></p><p class="c31"><span class="c66">3. Relaci&oacute;n clasificada de los gastos, meses durante los que ha recibido el servicio la alumna/o, con identificaci&oacute;n de la factura, fecha de emisi&oacute;n e importe pagado por la alumna/o.</span></p><hr style="page-break-before:always;display:none;"><p class="c39 c27"><span class="c6 c10 c78"></span></p><p class="c39 c27"><span class="c6 c78 c10"></span></p><p class="c25 c27"><span class="c6 c22"></span></p><p class="c11"><span class="c6 c22"></span></p><p class="c25"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 63.33px; height: 94.07px;"><img alt="" src="images/image1.png" style="width: 63.33px; height: 94.07px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c11"><span class="c6 c22"></span></p><p class="c36 c27"><span class="c6 c22"></span></p><table class="c33"><tr class="c29"><td class="c55" colspan="1" rowspan="3"><p class="c17"><span class="c24 c26">3.1</span></p></td><td class="c0" colspan="1" rowspan="2"><p class="c17"><span class="c24 c26">SERVICIO</span></p></td><td class="c103 c77" colspan="1" rowspan="2"><p class="c13"><span class="c24 c26">PERIODO</span></p><p class="c87"><span class="c24 c26">(m&aacute;x. 10 meses)</span></p></td><td class="c38" colspan="3" rowspan="1"><p class="c17"><span class="c24 c26">FACTURA</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c29"><td class="c61" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c17"><span class="c24 c26">N&Uacute;MERO</span></p></td><td class="c40" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c17"><span class="c24 c26">FECHA</span></p></td><td class="c9" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c17"><span class="c24 c26">IMPORTE</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c21"><td class="c56" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c34"><s